PRIVACY POLICY – AGECALC PRO
Last updated: April 27, 2026

This Privacy Policy explains how AgeCalc Pro ("the App") handles information.

1. INFORMATION WE COLLECT
The App does not collect, transmit, or share any personal information.
All data you enter (dates, names for birthday tracking) is stored exclusively
on your device's local storage and is never sent to any server.

2. DATA STORAGE
• Birthday names and dates are saved locally in the app's private database.
• No data leaves your device.
• Uninstalling the app permanently deletes all stored data.

3. PERMISSIONS
The App requires NO special permissions (no camera, no location, no internet,
no contacts, no storage access).

4. THIRD-PARTY SERVICES
The App does not use any third-party analytics, advertising SDKs, or crash
reporting services.

5. CHILDREN'S PRIVACY
The App is suitable for all ages. We do not knowingly collect data from anyone.

6. CHANGES TO THIS POLICY
If we update this policy, the new version will be posted with a revised date.

